                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d491">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Peirce</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Embassy of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">St. Petersburg</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1900-08-27">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 27, 1900</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Peirce reports that the Russian Government approve Li Hung Chang’s
                    appointment, but that he should be required to exhibit quite satisfactory full
                    powers from a de facto government before beginning negotiations.)</p>
            </div>
